    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Ambrane - Multiple Openings",
    "description": "Grow your career with Ambrane! We are hiring a Marketplace Manager for our Ranchi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Ambrane:\nAmbrane is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ambrane!",
